// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/msXGzB circular connector sdf by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdX3WH Interior Distance Detect Errors
// (using iq's sdf visualization)

// Connect two offset lines by two circles. Exact euclidean sdf.

// tags: sdf, circle, distance, euclidean, circular, offset, continuous, exact, c1, connector

